    "description": "<p>HiSPACE PTE. LTD. aiming to provide installation, testing and commissioning of Air-Conditioning and Mechanical Ventilation (ACMV) System, Building management system (BMS) &amp; Engineering smoke control system (ESCS).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are one stop solution provider for ACMV system from predesign stage to post execution till completion of project, we also perform cost planning, lift cycle costing and cost control for our clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We also provide Comprehensive &amp; Non-comprehensive Service &amp; Maintenance for ACMV System.</p>",
